full_title: Clique by Kanye West, JAY-Z & Big Sean
title: Clique

description.plain: “Clique” is the third single off of G.O.O.D. Music’s compilation album, Cruel Summer, following “Mercy” and “New God Flow”. The beat was produced by Hit-Boy (his second credit for a song featuring The Throne), Kanye West, Anthony Kilhoffer and Noah Goldstein.
